PLACEHOLDER — Replace this file with your production Ed25519 public key in PEM format.

To generate a key pair:
  openssl genpkey -algorithm Ed25519 -out urot_privkey_gen0.pem
  openssl pkey -in urot_privkey_gen0.pem -pubout -out urot_pubkey_gen0.pem

The private key (urot_privkey_gen0.pem) must be kept secret and never placed
in this directory or committed to source control.

The manufacturing application detects placeholder and known example keys and
will display a warning if this file has not been replaced.
